{"tid":198670,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎傾下張衛健舊時啲劇","createTime":"2017-04-12T16:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T16:15:04.000Z","uid":41798,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"297e854e8bd451eca0241747512f1cb9529b8655","tid":198670,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"而家啲後生仔分鐘只係知佢扮孫悟空,<br />\n但佢舊時播親既電視劇真係叫好又叫座,<br />\n西遊記唔使講,<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得佢最正既三套係以下三套,而且片尾曲都係由張衛健唱,<br />\n仲要超好聽!<br />\n<br />\n1.小寶與康熙<br />\n<br />\n呢套都好出名,當時個個都識涼風有信,<br />\n某程度上佢改篇改到另一個故事咁,但個人覺得仲好睇過原著既鹿鼎記,<br />\n仲要有七個靚女,又有朱茵,陳法蓉(仲有無人記得佢?),仲有超可愛既大眼妹林心如!<br />\n真人仲揀埋可愛既小郡主沐劍屏-張茜做老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以話係所有鹿鼎記入面最多真真正正靚女既一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗情,仲有個義字!第一係義氣,第二係義氣,第三都係義氣! <br />\n<br />\n片尾曲-你愛我像誰<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cXPx96qKuM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6cXPx96qKuM&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=16b5d792\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cXPx96qKuM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.小魚兒與花無缺<br />\n<br />\n呢套睇張衛健大既都應該識,唔識都應該聽過,<br />\n又係有徐錦江<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,<br />\n仲要有謝霆峰花無缺,范冰冰鐵心蘭<br />\n當時喺亞視播,無線不得不用另一套好睇既劇同佢對憾,<br />\n係呀,當時兩邊互搶收視,啲劇集質素好正架,<br />\n唔似而家hea拍都得,<br />\n小魚兒花無缺兩兄弟兩兄弟既情,<br />\n小仙女蘇櫻十大惡人<br />\n仲有唔再打對台既徐錦江惡通天所付出既一切,<br />\n都離不開一個情字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n片尾曲-超人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ki8uKmKzk84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dki8uKmKzk84&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c51e9c68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ki8uKmKzk84</a><br />\n<br />\n3.盜海奇兵(又名:A計劃)<br />\n<br />\n又係亞視播,但當時既亞視已經收收地皮,所以呢套睇過既人更少,<br />\n今次主角兩兄弟又係張衛健同譚耀文,<br />\n又係一兵一賊,即係小寶同康熙既組合,<br />\n仲要有王晶元秋同埋呀嬌,<br />\n係呀,我無講錯你無聽錯,演員係王晶同呀嬌呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各方面都好出色,<br />\n但奈何劇情有少少似小寶與康熙,<br />\n而且唔止片尾曲正,連主題曲都一樣正!<br />\n但因為套野少人睇,歌都好少人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n片尾曲-給你的愛<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jHGzQp3mgEU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjHGzQp3mgEU&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c7b01c49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jHGzQp3mgEU</a><br />\n<br />\n主題曲-感動(張衛健+周華健合唱)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CXodwVqkyJ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCXodwVqkyJ0&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=359f20df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CXodwVqkyJ0</a>"},{"pid":"ddb8fca790d3036cf06a4e1d0ed1b9449f40db4a","tid":198670,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:30:01.000Z","msg":"我想講功夫足球<br />\n雖然好鳩但係好鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ca6ab85b4fd6f34fc96fad65271e495b577838","tid":198670,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:30:30.000Z","msg":"當然仲有好多劇都好睇啦,<br />\n少年方世玉,少年張豐,聚寶盆等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d091799e631333efbb222e2563bbd6b418d33d7e","tid":198670,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:31:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想講功夫足球<br />\n雖然好鳩但係好鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果個叫乜鳩大S慧星射球"},{"pid":"9c0340351c0474349606f79800a04810c75d4dea","tid":198670,"uid":3577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"早排睇番龍兄鼠弟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{