講功夫足球<br />\n雖然好鳩但係好鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好鳩，但果陣晚晚追<br />\n<br />\nbtw <br />\n<br />\n小寶與康熙真係無撚敵，歌好聽，女又正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢套都係因為張衛健先睇得落去,個劇本抄少林足球都算,<br />\n仲要個劇情真係好爛,同舊時啲劇既質素差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女又唔靚,係得佢同黃秋生有啲睇頭"},{"pid":"0ef3dfbb06d45b28f8ac8edbfe1c22c790d503f8","tid":198670,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊度有得睇返小寶與康熙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyoutude,但好似唔係全足本,有啲位cut咗,<br />\n搞到有啲劇情無交代,變成有犯駁位"},{"pid":"b7144d4434fcde7dfe42434ef6442525828ed468","tid":198670,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:44:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老友鬼鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實鬼戲要搞笑真係好容易，但而家tvb連咁簡單都做唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以話佢既成名作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff33f5a525a37abba26b4cbc226dab803647544","tid":198670,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:46:18.000Z","msg":"聚寶盆"},{"pid":"b2599579d489df01b5ae62cc12de6d13063a38bc","tid":198670,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想睇返老友鬼鬼 應該冇咩可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇過既巴打應該都年紀大了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 老友鬼鬼<br />\n日月神劍都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一太唔記得叫咩