r />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ki8uKmKzk84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dki8uKmKzk84&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c51e9c68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ki8uKmKzk84</a><br />\n<br />\n3.盜海奇兵(又名:A計劃)<br />\n<br />\n又係亞視播,但當時既亞視已經收收地皮,所以呢套睇過既人更少,<br />\n今次主角兩兄弟又係張衛健同譚耀文,<br />\n又係一兵一賊,即係小寶同康熙既組合,<br />\n仲要有王晶元秋同埋呀嬌,<br />\n係呀,我無講錯你無聽錯,演員係王晶同呀嬌呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各方面都好出色,<br />\n但奈何劇情有少少似小寶與康熙,<br />\n而且唔止片尾曲正,連主題曲都一樣正!<br />\n但因為套野少人睇,歌都好少人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n片尾曲-給你的愛<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jHGzQp3mgEU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjHGzQp3mgEU&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c7b01c49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jHGzQp3mgEU</a><br />\n<br />\n主題曲-感動(張衛健+周華健合唱)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CXodwVqkyJ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCXodwVqkyJ0&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=359f20df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CXodwVqkyJ0</a></blockquote><br />\n第一句話人後生仔只識孫悟空，以為你會講咩老友鬼鬼之類，點知你講d仲新d既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be35cf9e95c4fa1fb4b1afc2e513a388ac1c1dd6","tid":198670,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:56:23.000Z","msg":"小仙女BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d11a4fa5424877bb55c939d082bc43fd8a53ee","tid":198670,"uid":53522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:05:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想講功夫足球<br />\n雖然好鳩但係好鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果個叫